{"tid":735991,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵每年賺幾百億都唔開大個冷氣","createTime":"2018-07-10T02:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T10:12:47.000Z","uid":184822,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0601728e13a82779a0278a1fff3d94e359a02e14","tid":735991,"uid":184822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:15:55.000Z","msg":"日日經過中環同香港站<br />\n一出車廂就熱風撲臉,而且焗過棺材房<br />\n行輸送帶時成日都要忍住唔好出汗<br />\n但最後都失守，底褲都濕哂<br />\n好似夢遺咁<br />\n<br />\n其他站有時空氣中隱約瀰漫住其他乘客嘅汗味<br />\n間唔鐘仲會有屎味<br />\n加上高溫<br />\n形成咗又熱又酸臭嘅氣團<br />\n真係好撚恐怖<br />\n<br />\n港鐵我屌你老母，每年賺咁多都要慳冷錢<br />\n難為咗大汗同有濕疹嘅人"},{"pid":"dc4a373fe8fcb8e3389fdc33d8bd66a6780fd704","tid":735991,"uid":74171,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:21:03.000Z","msg":"問下啲環保撚點解咁鍾意叫人set 25度"},{"pid":"a3880692a8e7575ae0db4312ac8f1afea5cc09dd","tid":735991,"uid":19501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:22:05.000Z","msg":"大堂同月台例牌冇冷氣，有時連車廂都唔涼"},{"pid":"e883269a7a192dc0c23167d2ff28cf12939f3cdb","tid":735991,"uid":184822,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"dc4a373fe8fcb8e3389fdc33d8bd66a6780fd704","tid":735991,"uid":74171,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:21:03.000Z","msg":"問下啲環保撚點解咁鍾意叫人set 25度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:22:27.000Z","msg":"25度全祼瞓覺都濕哂啦"},{"pid":"5b1bc55db155df08d451e1d11d15052b02737a5e","tid":735991,"uid":190540,"like":3,"dislike":23,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:22:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53a374a24612e03bbc32e1160f5ad8e53f9c74e4","tid":735991,"uid":92017,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:45:56.000Z","msg":"臭閪環保團體既辦公室係咪唔開冷氣架<br />\n要全香港一齊受罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3532c2bb6cba4d84aea509401806aa643300c63a","tid":735991,"uid":25085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:47:34.000Z","msg":"熱死人"},{"pid":"90955b97071e69cf97